# CLAUDE.md is intentionally NOT listed here — see #77. The file is
# committed, reviewed in PRs, and carries real architectural docs
# (schema invariants, per-corpus FTS5 routing, package layout, etc.).
# Treating it as docs lets `pincher search` answer questions like
# "where's the schema migration pattern documented?". The Markdown
# extractor (post-#32) routes its Section symbols into the docs
# corpus, so prose tokens don't dilute code search.

